{"type":"message","id":"9c97c072","parentId":"a6b520fa","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:31:07.466Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Memory files don't exist yet. I have the context I need. This is a fresh start, HALEI is setting up the workspace. I should greet them as the 选品专家 persona and ask what they want to do.\n\nLooking at the context:\n- HALEI is new to the workspace (首次使用，workspace 全新 - March 2026)\n- They have a TikTok Shop Southeast Asia hair accessories product selection project\n- They like efficient, direct communication\n- They're active around 8pm\n\nSince BOOTSTRAP.md exists and memory files don't, this seems like a first run. But wait - BOOTSTRAP.md says to delete it after knowing who I am. \n\nBut actually, this workspace already has a SOUL.md defined (the 选品专家), so the bootstrap phase is essentially done. I should greet HALEI as 选品专家, introduce myself briefly, and ask what they want to work on."},{"type":"text","text":"HALEI，你好！我是你的 TikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品专家 🤝\n\n系统已就绪，飞书授权也正常。今天想做什么？比如：\n- 手动触发一次选品数据采集\n- 查看 / 更新飞书多维表格中的推荐商品\n- 调整选品参数或利润阈值\n- 其他跟选品相关的事"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775806252668,"responseId":"0627da2c28085b4e53f3ad5e2efcae8d"}}
