{"type":"message","id":"f69c1e12","parentId":"3a492584","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:31:20.532Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 15:31:18 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52be3a9e00b8c44d5c25dbbfc49]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52be3a9e00b8c44d5c25dbbfc49\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 15:31 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n使用vibesurf 访问  [seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com](http://seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com/)  这个地址，"}],"timestamp":1775806280526}}
