{"type":"message","id":"7e8c5b59","parentId":"376a32ab","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:38:25.308Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 16:38:23 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52bf2113d4b4b30be91be5014c6]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52bf2113d4b4b30be91be5014c6\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 16:38 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n现在的数据获取流程是这样的，我简单跟你说一下。\n\n我们会从以下两个主要的网站和三个途径来获取数据：\n1. TK后台：\n  a. 商品销量排行榜（包含短视频、商品卡、直播数据）\n  b. 商品机会（官方后台）\n2. 付费渠道：EchoTik（E C H O T I K）\n\n因为我们这部分对数据筛选之后，后续需要将数据存在飞书表格里，包括来源和链接。准确地说，后续我们还要把图片去1688上进行识别。\n\n就在这个流程里，我们使用的方式跟现有的流程有什么区别？这是第一。\n\n第二，就是你需要看一下驱动WebSurf这个可视化浏览器的必要性"}],"timestamp":1775810305299}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d041820","parentId":"7e8c5b59","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:39:02.406Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HALEI is asking two questions:\n\n1. What's the difference between his data acquisition flow and the current/built-in flow in my system\n2. Whether we need VibeSurf (the visual browser) for this workflow\n\nLet me analyze his flow:\n\nHis flow:\n- TK后台 (TikTok Seller backend):排行榜 + 商品机会\n- EchoTik (paid third-party platform)\n- Data gets filtered/筛选 → stored in Feishu table → then image search on 1688\n\nMy current SOUL.md mentions:\n- 数据源：TikTok Shop 后台/泰国越南站点热搜榜、InfluTalk、EchoTik 行业数据\n\n\n- 妙手/店小秘ERP采集、1688 同款比对\n\nSo the main gaps are: I don't have access to the actual TikTok backend pages or EchoTik's paid data, I'm lacking the specific ranking data he mentioned (short video, product card, live streaming), and I don't currently handle the image-to-1688 reverse image search step that's part of his workflow.\n\nFor the VibeSurf question, I need to think through when browser automation actually makes sense versus when simpler tools would work better.\n\nVibeSurf makes sense when I need to handle sites requiring login credentials or captchas, interact with dynamic JavaScript-heavy pages, or perform visual comparisons of product images. But if the data sources provide APIs or the information is publicly accessible, web search and web fetch would be more efficient. The 1688 reverse image search is a case where VibeSurf could add value since it likely requires visual browsing capability."},{"type":"text","text":"好问题，帮你梳理清楚。\n\n---\n\n## 一、现有流程 vs 我的内置流程\n\n| 环节 | 你的实际流程 | 我的内置流程 |\n|------|-------------|-------------|\n| **数据源** | TK后台（排行榜+商品机会）+ EchoTik | EchoTik / 热搜榜 |\n| **热销数据** | ✅ 有（短视频/商品卡/直播三渠道） | ⚠️ 需要 EchoTik API |\n| **商品机会** | ✅ 有（官方后台） | ❌ 未接入 |\n| **1688比价** | ✅ 人工/ERP比对 | ✅ 理论支持（1688采购链接） |\n| **图片识款** | ✅ 1688以图搜款 | ❌ 未集成 |\n| **数据落地** | ✅ 飞书多维表格 | ✅ 飞书多维表格 |\n\n**核心差距：**\n1. **TK后台排行榜 + 商品机会** — 这两个目前我没有直接的 API 接入方式，需要通过 VibeSurf 浏览器访问\n2. **图片→1688以图搜款** — 完整流程未闭环，VibeSurf 可以处理\n\n---\n\n## 二、VibeSurf 的必要性评估\n\n| 场景 | 是否需要 VibeSurf | 原因 |\n|------|------------------|------|\n| TK后台排行榜 | ✅ 需要 | 需要登录，数据未公开 |\n| EchoTik 付费数据 | ⚠️ 可选 | 有 API 则不需要，没有则需要浏览器抓取 |\n| 1688以图搜款 | ✅ 需要 | 以图搜图是纯浏览器操作 |\n| 公开数据获取 | ❌ 不需要 | web_fetch / web_search 更快更便宜 |\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\n**VibeSurf 不是所有环节都必要**，但对于你流程中的关键瓶颈是它最适合的工具：\n- TK后台数据（无 API）\n- 图片识款（1688以图搜）\n\n建议：**保留 VibeSurf，主要用于这两个环节**，其余优先走 API 或 web 工具。\n\n你目前 EchoTik 是走 API 还是浏览器？确认后我可以给你一个更具体的数据打通方案。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775810305315,"responseId":"0627ea01c4d4c7825b81f9c5ec20083c"}}
